SP.P:
Honest musk-cod, twill not be so stitched toge∣ther;
take that, and that, and belie no Ladies loue:
sweare no more by Iesu: this Madam, that Ladie;
hence goe, forsweare the presence, trauaile three years


to bury this bastinado: auoide, puffe paste, auoide.

Truely, I haue strained a note aboue Ela, for a de∣uise;


looke you, tis a faire rul'd singing booke: the
word, Perfect, if it were prickt.
